title: 30-MINUTE FULL BODY WEIGHT LOSS – SIMPLE WORKOUT
description:
Today’s workout video is an easy, beginner's workout that consists of very doable routines that will work your entire body and all the major muscles you have to burn the underlying and stubborn fats spread throughout your body. 

These routines are all body-weight exercises meaning you don’t need to use any equipment at all--just your bodies!

Good luck and let’s get started! ❤️💪﻿

**If you want to be notified when I upload a new video, make sure to subscribe to our channel. I upload new videos everyday from Sunday to Friday!
